snippet.title: Euclidean Skies Official Trailer - iOS
snippet.description:
Download Euclidean Skies on the App Store:
https://itunes.apple.com/app/euclidean-skies/id1404253683

Euclidean Skies is the successor to the highly acclaimed game Euclidean Lands.

It combines marvelous architecture and turn-based movements to create a beautiful world with mind-bending puzzles.
